2) TROUBLESHOOTING


1) INFO
Set of scripts/configs to prepare debian packages [for deployment] from source code.
Created with git/github repos in mind. Additional READMEs in subdirs.

Subdirs:
jenkins - contains readme, scripts and such related to configuring jenkins
reprepro - contains readme, scripts and such related to configuring reprepro


All scripts & bugs, if another is not mentioned is written by Roman Ovchinnikov <coolthecold@gmail.com>


2) TROUBLESHOOTING
IF IN TROUBLE use "bash -x path/to/script/name" - this will reveal a lot of details.

